it Nabs Ingrid Michaelson's Music & More|last=Pace|first=Lilly|date=November 21, 2019|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|url-status=live|access-date=November 22, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Paine\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.musicweek.com/publishing/read/the-voice-of-her-generation-kobalt-inks-global-deal-with-mxmtoon/078137|title='The voice of her generation': Kobalt inks global deal with Mxmtoon|last=Paine|first=Andre|date=November 19, 2019|website=[[Music Week]]|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122131737/https://www.musicweek.com/publishing/read/the-voice-of-her-generation-kobalt-inks-global-deal-with-mxmtoon/078137|archive-date=November 21, 2019|access-date=November 22, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PBTE\">{{Cite web|title=plum blossom (the edits)|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/plum-blossom-the-edits-single/1458823614|website=[[Apple Music]]|access-date=August 30, 2019|url-status = live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Rindner\">{{Cite web|title=Sincerity Isn\u2019t Scary For mxmtoon|url=https://nylon.com/mxmtoon-you-tube-interview|website=[[Nylon (magazine)|Nylon]]|last=Rindner|first=Grant|date=September 17, 2019|access-date=December 23, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RYM\">{{Cite web|url=https://rateyourmusic.com/artist/mxmtoon|title=mxmtoon discography|website=[[Rate Your Music]]|access-date=August 30, 2019|url-status = live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sideline\">{{Cite web|title=The Sideline \u2013 Single by mxmtoon|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/the-sideline-single/1458638435|website=[[Apple Music]]|access-date=August 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721101256/https://music.apple.com/us/album/the-sideline-single/1458638435|archive-date=July 21, 2019|url-status = live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sidewalk\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I856GQRs5QU|title=MXMTOON Interview- coming out bisexual, ethnicity identity problems, hiding music from parents|last=Engel|first=Lauren|website=[[YouTub